trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en referanse til en discovery-dokumentet.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: XML Web services discovery involves discovering the available XML Web services given an URL.
trans-unit.target: XML-Web services discovery innebærer å oppdage tilgjengelig XML-webtjenestene gitt en URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: The URL typically points to a discovery document, which usually has a.disco file name extension.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen peker vanligvis til discovery-dokumentet, som vanligvis har a.disco filtype.

trans-unit.source: The discovery document contains references to information about the existance of XML Web services, such as Service Descriptions, XML Schema Definition language (XSD) schemas, or other discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Discovery-dokumentet inneholder referanser til informasjon om eksistens for XML-webtjenester, for eksempel beskrivelser av tjenesten, XML-skjemadefinisjon språket (XSD) skjemaer eller andre discovery-dokumenter.

trans-unit.target: Ref-egenskapen er en URL-adresse, for eksempel http://www.contoso.com/MyWebService.disco for de fleste referanser.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that all referenced documents within the discovery document are valid.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer at alle refererte dokumenter i discovery-dokumentet er gyldige.

trans-unit.source: Unless you specifically need to resolve the individual references of a <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference> object, you should invoke the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A> or <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A> methods of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du skal spesielt individuelle referanser for et <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>objekt, må du aktivere den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A>metodene for <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveOneLevel%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.ResolveAll%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryDocumentReference>

trans-unit.source: This method resolves all references to discovery documents, XSD schemas, and Service Descriptions in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> and any references found in referring discovery documents.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden løser alle referanser til discovery dokumenter, XSD-skjema og tjenestebeskrivelser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>for <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A>og referanser i refererer discovery dokumenter.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference.ClientProtocol%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.References%2A>
